Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:04.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（异步研究所）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:10.45,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（基洛纳区调查：档案446 — 纳伦·沃恩\N1990年6月19日\N美国能源部）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 好\N{\rEng}Okay, okay, okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对\N{\rEng}{\rEng}Yes... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对 快点 快点 没错 没错\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, come on... Come on, yes! Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,到了 到了 到了\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了\N{\rEng}Here we go, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好 该死\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay. Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能用 能用 一定得能用\N{\rEng}Work. Work. Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,基准组... 好...\N{\rEng}Standard... Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,基准组 你们...你们能收到吗？\N{\rEng}Standard, can you- can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是纳伦\N{\rEng}This is Naren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我 呃...\N{\rEng}And I've, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟其他人走散了\N{\rEng}I've been separated, uh, from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该没事\N{\rEng}And I think I'm okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我现在到底在哪儿\N{\rEng}but I'm not sure where I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没走到过这么深 所以我也...\N{\rEng}I've never been out this far before, so I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才有个...\N{\rEng}There was this, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看清 可是 呃...\N{\rEng}I didn't get a good look at it, but there was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有别的东西\N{\rEng}there's something else in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快来\N{\rEng}I need you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？快来接我 求你们了\N{\rEng}Okay? I need you guys to get me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 快来把我弄出去\N{\rEng}Fuck, I need you guys to come out and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦来接我 求你们了 基准组\N{\rEng}Can you... can you come, please, standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了吗？\N{\rEng}Standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\N{\rEng}Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 该死\N{\rEng}Fuck! Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 搞什么鬼？\N{\rEng}Oh, shit... What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（需无用信...）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 完了 完了\N{\rEng}Fuck! Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,完了\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 完了 完了\N{\rEng}Fuck, fuck, fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:55.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}《后室》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:33.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（山脊公寓楼盘）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都有自己的死循环 固有的习惯...\N{\rEng}We all have our loops, our habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,总是重蹈覆辙...\N{\rEng}...behaviors that keep us walking in circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总是用同样的办法 一遍又一遍\N{\rEng}...reaching for the same solutions over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:12.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（克船长的家具帝国）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,却指望能走出新路\N{\rEng}thinking each time they'll take you somewhere new.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但没用\N{\rEng}But they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟\N{\rEng}And still,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,神经通路就爱走阻力最小的路径\N{\rEng}it's the neural pathway of least resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.75,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（奸商）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你建立了心理防线\N{\rEng}A path you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候 这套防线保护了你\N{\rEng}It's the one that kept you safe when you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你学会了抢在被伤害之前\N{\rEng}You learned to push people away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,把别人推开\N{\rEng}before they could hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rEng}And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你都成年了\N{\rEng}as an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.69,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（逾期通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还是留在原地\N{\rEng}you're still stuck right where you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个人\N{\rEng}Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我有人陪啊\N{\rEng}I mean, I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我有店员 还有顾客\N{\rEng}I have employees and... customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说有人陪 我说的是只有一个人\N{\rEng}I didn't say lonely. I said alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 是 但是...\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我老是伤人\N{\rEng}I hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想 可我脑回路就这样\N{\rEng}I don't want to. It's just the way I'm wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可能就该把自己关起来\N{\rEng}So maybe I deserve to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谁活该把自己关着吗？\N{\rEng}Do you think anyone deserves to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不好 但怎么说呢\N{\rEng}I don't know, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这样也挺好\N{\rEng}maybe it's not such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,自我封闭...\N{\rEng}Being alone feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已经刻进骨子里了\N{\rEng}deeply ingrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\rEng}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你有梦想 但老是受挫\N{\rEng}You've had dreams and a lot of resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,身边也没人支持你\N{\rEng}not a lot of support in realizing those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当伤害变成了...\N{\rEng}And when we've experienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一次次家常便饭\N{\rEng}hurt again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会习惯性地想\N{\rEng}we start to expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“哦 这路我熟”\N{\rEng}It's like, "Oh, I know this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,“下场一定是一样的”\N{\rEng}I know where it goes."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\N{\rEng}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想摆脱这个死循环\N{\rEng}are you interested in forging a new path
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走出一条不同的路？\N{\rEng}and see where that leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来都来了 就试试吧\N{\rEng}Why not? You know, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要不咱们重温一下...\N{\rEng}So I want to revisit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,之前练过的那个...\N{\rEng}an exercise we've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,角色扮演\N{\rEng}The role play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 演戏那套？ - 对\N{\rEng}- Oh, the acting thing? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得太丢人了 - 我懂\N{\rEng}- I feel stupid doing that. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然还有点时间 就....\N{\rEng}But we have a few minutes. Let's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,试一下吧 稍微试试\N{\rEng}Yeah, let's try. A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们先定个场景\N{\rEng}Let's set the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回到芭芭拉离开你的那晚\N{\rEng}Let's go back to the night that Barbara left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说她把我从我自己家给撵出去的那晚？\N{\rEng}You mean the night she kicked me out of my own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我演我自己\N{\rEng}I'm playing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我演芭芭拉\N{\rEng}And I'll be Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了 那可是我的房子\N{\rEng}It is my house, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷都是我在还\N{\rEng}I'm the one paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道 - 好吧\N{\rEng}- I know. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那...\N{\rEng}Okay, so, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我回家晚了 具体几点我忘了\N{\rEng}I got home late. I don't know how late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候她已经睡了 应该是半夜了\N{\rEng}Uh... She was already asleep. Maybe midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她一般睡得早... 算了 这不重要\N{\rEng}She usually goes to bed before... It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是我当时在厨房 额...\N{\rEng}The point is, I was in the kitchen, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有个杯子 我把杯子打碎了\N{\rEng}the glass, I broke the glass, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她听见动静跑下来 然后...\N{\rEng}she comes running down to see what happened, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就闹起来了\N{\rEng}things escalated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你当时什么感受？\N{\rEng}And how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时...\N{\rEng}Well, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时喝多了...\N{\rEng}I was drunk, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我觉得自己挺蠢的 你懂吧\N{\rEng}I-I felt stupid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就火了 因为...因为我把杯子打碎了\N{\rEng}I was angry, because... because I broke the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你能对着我再说一遍吗？\N{\rEng}Can you say that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对着你 对着芭芭拉？ - 对\N{\rEng}- Uh, what, to-to Barbara? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 把你吵醒了\N{\rEng}Um... I'm sorry that I woke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你能早点回家\N{\rEng}Maybe if you'd come home earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们今晚本该待在一起的\N{\rEng}we could have spent the evening together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我在加班 你懂的\N{\rEng}No, I was... I was working, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下班后我就直接回来了\N{\rEng}I came straight home after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,诚实点吧\N{\rEng}Be honest with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上那酒气我都闻得见\N{\rEng}I can smell it on your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去喝了一点啤酒\N{\rEng}I had a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一点是多少？\N{\rEng}Define a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 今天太累了\N{\rEng}Well, it was a hard day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我得喝点放松放松\N{\rEng}I needed to wind down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不成天在放松吗？\N{\rEng}All you ever do is wind down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,成天呆在那店里\N{\rEng}You're always at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要孩子 对吧？\N{\rEng}You want kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们都想要 - 但你要知道...\N{\rEng}- We both do. - Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,养孩子得花钱\N{\rEng}having a family takes money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人去挣钱\N{\rEng}which means someone has to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除非现在当学生\N{\rEng}Unless being a professional student
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也能算份工作了\N{\rEng}is considered a job these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这么说 你知道我得休学一段时间\N{\rEng}That's not fair. You know I had to take time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己跟不上 凭什么怪我\N{\rEng}Well, it's not my fault if you can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,连法学院都搞不定\N{\rEng}How are you going to be a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还想怎么当律师？\N{\rEng}if you can't even handle law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当你这个三十岁的“大一新生”\N{\rEng}Who do you think pays for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校里到处瞎逛时\N{\rEng}while you're gallivanting around campus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也不想想谁在供你上学？\N{\rEng}like a 30-year-old freshman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,提示你一下 那就是我\N{\rEng}I'll give you a hint: it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你上学是我供 休学也是我供\N{\rEng}I pay for your school, I pay for your time off school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,连住这儿都还是我在供\N{\rEng}I pay for the roof over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能说句话吗？ - 不 我还没说完\N{\rEng}- Can I talk now? - No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒想知道 要是你真混到毕业了\N{\rEng}Because I'd like to know, what do you think happens
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,又会发生什么？\N{\rEng}if you do manage to graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,生个娃 然后继续把账单甩给我吗？\N{\rEng}You know, you pop out a kid, then leave me with the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你天天忙你的第一份工作\N{\rEng}Or am I stuck at home changing diapers because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我在家里给娃换屎尿？\N{\rEng}you're too busy working for the first time in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这话太过分了 - 我只是说实话\N{\rEng}- Now you're being cruel. - I'm being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来这就是你的追求\N{\rEng}I thought that's what you always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你没考上建筑师 并不代表...\N{\rEng}Just because you didn't get to be an architect doesn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老子就是建筑师！\N{\rEng}I am a fucking architect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以得成天在那破店里卖这些玩意儿\N{\rEng}God damn it, I'm just stuck selling shit furniture because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为某个懒猪在家混吃等死 根本不肯出力\N{\rEng}someone won't get off their fat fucking ass and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 现在感觉怎么样？\N{\rEng}How do you feel, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我在跟谁说话呢？\N{\rEng}Who am I talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 和我 此刻 此地 - 哦 你啊 好吧\N{\rEng}- Me, here, now. - You? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\rEng}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不是有意说...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I didn't mean to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 刚才发火了\N{\rEng}...you know, get angry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,情绪失控了那种\N{\rEng}or lose my temper or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,练习的目的就在这儿\N{\rEng}That's the purpose of the whole exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个不错的开始\N{\rEng}This is a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,正视你的感受\N{\rEng}To feel what you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后慢慢找出一条新路\N{\rEng}and then learn to identify a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你的反应其实很正常\N{\rEng}Your reaction was actually quite normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 我就这德行\N{\rEng}Well, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 伙计们 瞧瞧这儿啊！\N{\rEng}Well, ahoy there, mateys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还打算把金币全砸在那些冤大头家具上？\N{\rEng}Tired of spending your hard-earned doubloons on overpriced furniture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想买惊掉下巴的跳海价吗？\N{\rEng}Looking for deals that'll shiver your timbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快来克船长的家具帝国！\N{\rEng}Then come on down to Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,圣克拉拉谷的头号家具大卖场\N{\rEng}the Santa Clara Valley's favorite warehouse and showrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.59,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【圣克拉拉谷：位于美国西部】
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卧室 客厅 餐厅 书房 浴室\N{\rEng}You'll find bedrooms, living rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全屋家具 应有尽有！\N{\rEng}dinettes, dens and bathrooms aplenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,刚买房的？来这儿就对了！\N{\rEng}First-time homeowners? We've got ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,新当爹妈的？\N{\rEng}New parents looking for Billy's first crib?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来这就对了！\N{\rEng}We've got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,时髦现代样样全\N{\rEng}From the latest in modern design
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,经典复古通通有\N{\rEng}to the classic styles of yesteryear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,价格低到没对手\N{\rEng}it's all here and it's all a steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 波莉？\N{\rEng}What's that, Polly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,信用卡里钱不够？\N{\rEng}You're worried about credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈！在克船长这儿 钱不够 没问题！\N{\rEng}Ha! Cap'n Clark says no credit, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快来畅游顶级家具海洋\N{\rEng}Sail the high seas of high quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把钱的问题统统抛在脑后\N{\rEng}and leave your money problems at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就来店里\N{\rEng}Walk in today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把梦想直接搬回家！\N{\rEng}and get your dream sectional lounger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,桌椅板凳 灯具摆件随便挑！\N{\rEng}kitchen table, floor lamp, and bed frame here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,克船长的家具帝国\N{\rEng}at Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就在680号公路出口 国会路和麦基路口\N{\rEng}located at Capitol and McKee, just off the 680.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿吼！赶紧过来...\N{\rEng}Arr! Walk in today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,翘起二郎腿\N{\rEng}...kick your feet back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当你的家具大王！\N{\rEng}and enjoy an empire of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 国王得有王座\N{\rEng}For every sultan deserves a throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的专属王座 就在这儿等着你\N{\rEng}and we've got one with your name on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就在克船长的...\N{\rEng}here at Cap'n Clark's--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卧槽\N{\rEng}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 没事吧？ - 快把相机关了\N{\rEng}- Clark, you good? - Turn the camera off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 拍得好 这种花絮才有趣\N{\rEng}No, no, it's good. It's outtake stuff, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶紧给老子关掉 - 好吧...我的天\N{\rEng}- Turn the fucking camera off. - Okay... Jesus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 要帮忙吗？\N{\rEng}You, uh, you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我自己来\N{\rEng}No, I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\rEng}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还要重拍吗？ - 不拍了\N{\rEng}- Are we going again, or...? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 去开门营业吧\N{\rEng}Kat, you can open the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早就开了\N{\rEng}We've been open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:34.20,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 我还是没搞懂\N{\rEng}You know, dude, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:38.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（结束南非种族隔离）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你演的是海盗还是国王？\N{\rEng}Are you, like, a pirate or a sultan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最好还是明确一下 - 我是个...闭嘴\N{\rEng}- Just be good to establish it. - I'm a... Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:41.79,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（结束南非种族隔离）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,刨花板做的破椅子\N{\rEng}Piece of cheap particleboard bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这东西弄走 听到没？\N{\rEng}Clear this stuff up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:04.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（1990年 6月）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 查出来没？\N{\rEng}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,电表没问题\N{\rEng}Meter reads fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,电费要是高 只能是你自己用得多\N{\rEng}If your bill's coming in high, that's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那跳电的事怎么说 打烊后就出现\N{\rEng}What about the outages? That happens after hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没准是荧光灯出问题 导致跳闸了\N{\rEng}Don't know. Fluorescents must be tripping a breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一打烊我就把顶灯都关了\N{\rEng}I turn the overheads off when the store closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还没闪之前就关了\N{\rEng}before the power gets weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果真是那样 电费不该更少吗？\N{\rEng}Anyway, wouldn't that just make the bills go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,配电箱在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where's your breaker box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我不是专家\N{\rEng}I'm no expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但我之前看过了 没看出什么问题\N{\rEng}but I checked earlier, and everything looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说灯会闪 - 对 整个店都闪\N{\rEng}- You said the lights flicker. - Yeah, the whole store does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？ - 只是不一起闪\N{\rEng}- Huh. - Just not at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有一晚是楼上\N{\rEng}One night, I lose the power upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下一晚就变成了楼下 完全没规律\N{\rEng}Next night, it's down here. There's no rhyme or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁装的这鬼东西？\N{\rEng}Who the hell installed this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子买来时 回路就这么走的\N{\rEng}Well, the building came wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点年头 但也不至于不能用\N{\rEng}I mean, it's dated, but it's not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（克拉克）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你来看看这个\N{\rEng}Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,之前没这东西\N{\rEng}That wasn't there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...\N{\rEng}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是我没注意到 我不是专家\N{\rEng}maybe I didn't notice. Like I say, I'm no expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为...为什么是斜着的？\N{\rEng}Why-why is it... why is it going that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,应该问问\N{\rEng}Better question:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西到底连到哪儿了\N{\rEng}what is it even connected to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\N{\rEng}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 楼上灯怎么样？\N{\rEng}Kat! How's the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有反应吗？\N{\rEng}Anything happen up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么搞的\N{\rEng}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老鼠又来了\N{\rEng}The rat's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 灯还正常吧 - 正常\N{\rEng}- But the power's on. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为咱们已经把老鼠给干掉了\N{\rEng}I thought we killed the rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们才干掉了一只\N{\rEng}We killed  "a"  rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就是问题原因吗？ - 没道理啊\N{\rEng}- So is this the problem? - Don't see how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,电路根本不走这里\N{\rEng}Power can't even go through this part of the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它纯粹是...\N{\rEng}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙出现在这\N{\rEng}there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,像被哪个笨蛋随便塞进去的\N{\rEng}Like some schmo just stuck it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否觉得生活像被隔在了一层玻璃之后？\N{\rEng}Do you ever feel like you're living behind glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看着世界在眼前上演\N{\rEng}Watching life happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,自己却只能旁观？\N{\rEng}but never really stepping into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 是时候打开心灵之窗了\N{\rEng}Maybe it's time to open the window within.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以重新定义自己的人生\N{\rEng}You can be the author of your own design
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每个人 都值得拥有另一次机会\N{\rEng}because we all deserve another chance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让梦想重新启航\N{\rEng}to fulfill our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你相信改变是可能的\N{\rEng}The moment you believe change is possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你就已经开始了这段旅程\N{\rEng}you've already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,立即订购《心灵之窗》\N{\rEng}Order The Window Within
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(《心灵之窗》)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,以及配套的三辑音频课程\N{\rEng}and the companion three-part audio program,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（突破障碍 掌控人生\N打破那扇窗）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,《引导之门》 均由玛丽·克莱因医生倾力呈现\N{\rEng}Guided Openings, by Dr. Mary Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.87,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（三辑音频课程）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现价24.95美元 运费另计\N{\rEng}Available now for $24.95 plus shipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请拨打1-800-555-0199\N{\rEng}Call 1-800-555-0199.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（克里斯·弗格森公司出品）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开辟一条新路 永远不晚\N{\rEng}It's never too late to forge a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.43,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【克里斯·弗格森：《后室》电影制片人】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“你居然还在信任纸质文件夹”\N{\rEng}"So, you're still trusting paper folders,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“贴错标签的磁带 还有个谁拿把钥匙”\N{\rEng}"mislabeled tapes, and a locked filing cabinet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“都能开的文件柜？”\N{\rEng}"that anyone with a spare key can open?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“信息决定企业的生死”\N{\rEng}"Your business runs on information,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“但大多数公司却把数据当成了堆杂物...”\N{\rEng}"yet most companies treat their data like clutter..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个信号不是小行星\N{\rEng}That small blip is not an asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是一艘飞船 它咬住我们了\N{\rEng}It's a spaceship, and it's on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:28.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（1970年圣克鲁斯现代主义建筑设计论坛）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它在靠近 - 不可能 里格娜\N{\rEng}- It's getting closer. - Impossible, Rigna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可能发现我们 雷达隐身还开着呢\N{\rEng}They couldn't have spotted us. We have our radar shield on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 长官 但他们追上来了\N{\rEng}I know that, sir, but they are gaining on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,难道地球人有某种秘密设备\N{\rEng}Is it possible Earth has a secret device
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,能穿透我们的雷达隐身罩？\N{\rEng}that can penetrate our radar shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾\N{\rEng}Piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“为什么 你要这样对待自己？”\N{\rEng}"Why did you do this to yourself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“你是怎么来到这里的？”\N{\rEng}"How did you get here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“你的意识 就像一个装满记忆的房间”\N{\rEng}"Your consciousness is a room full of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“它在时刻重构 在无限演变”\N{\rEng}"that is constantly evolving."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（收音机 磁带）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“在现实生活中”\N{\rEng}"But as you walk through life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“缺乏引导的心灵会开始筑墙”\N{\rEng}"the untrained mind can start to build walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,“建立屏障”\N{\rEng}"put up barriers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“隔绝外界”\N{\rEng}"to protect itself from the outside world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“这是本能反应”\N{\rEng}"It's a natural response."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们常常对此毫无察觉”\N{\rEng}"Something we are often unaware of."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“但久而久之”\N{\rEng}"But if gone unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,“你会发现 自己被囚禁了”\N{\rEng}"it can leave you feeling trapped."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“你会说服自己”\N{\rEng}"You can become convinced that the world outside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“外面的世界不需要你”\N{\rEng}"is better off without you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“你会告诉自己 自己不配被爱”\N{\rEng}"That you never deserve the relationships you've had."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“于是 你只能蜷缩在窗后”\N{\rEng}"Resigned to watch your life unfold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“当个旁观者 静静地看着生活上演”\N{\rEng}"from behind a lone window."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“让我来帮你打开”\N{\rEng}"I can help you open it now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“因为窗户根本没锁”\N{\rEng}"because the window isn't locked."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“门也没有封死”\N{\rEng}"The latch was never broken."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,“准备好跨过去了吗？”\N{\rEng}"Are you ready to step through?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,“去夺回属于你的东西”\N{\rEng}"So that you can reclaim that which was once yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,“去重新主宰你的生命”\N{\rEng}"and take back control of your life."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“去过你想过的人生”\N{\rEng}"The life you want to be living."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“卸下过去的沉重”\N{\rEng}"Unburdened by the traumas of the past."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,“走出那些你亲手打造的围墙”\N{\rEng}"Free of the confines you had built."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...所以我想...\N{\rEng}...to leave, and so I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“开辟一条属于你自己的路”\N{\rEng}"And free to choose a path of your own design."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（家庭牙科诊所 米莱服饰）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（停车）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“嘿 牛仔们 快瞧这边！”\N{\rEng}"Well, hey there, cowboys and cowgirls!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“想在格兰德河这块地盘”\N{\rEng}"Are you looking to rustle up the best deals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:19.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【格兰德河：位于美国南部】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“抢到最便宜的家具吗？”\N{\rEng}"this side of the Rio Grande?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,混球\N{\rEng}Prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“咿吼！快来大韦恩家具店！”\N{\rEng}"Well, yeehaw, I say yeehaw!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“买了我们的餐厅套装”\N{\rEng}"Here at Big Wayne's, our dining room sets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“就跟挖到金矿一样！”\N{\rEng}"are gonna make you feel like you just struck gold."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“别去管那些破店”\N{\rEng}"So don't even think about going anyplace else."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“认准大韦恩 认准金色招...”\N{\rEng}"Big Wayne's, just look for the golden--"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（大韦恩家具店）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么...\N{\rEng}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:57.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（由此下楼）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:01.14,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（由此下楼）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看老子怎么修理你\N{\rEng}Fuck! Piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.38,0:29:06.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（车停）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.69,0:29:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（粤语）“各位好吗？祝各位平安健康快乐”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.27,0:29:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,（阿卡德语）“愿一切都很好”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.67,0:29:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,（俄语）“你好 欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.70,0:30:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（泰语）“远方土地的朋友们 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.57,0:30:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（泰语）“在这片土地上的我们 向你们所有人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（阿拉伯语）“我们向星际中的朋友们致以问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.94,0:30:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（阿拉伯语）“但愿时间能让我们相聚”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,（罗马尼亚语）“向大家问好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.14,0:30:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）“大家好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.25,0:30:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（缅甸语）“你们好吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.66,0:30:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（希伯来语）“你好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）“你好 向大家致敬”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.28,0:30:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）“女士们先生们 晚上好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.84,0:30:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）“再见...”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.14,0:30:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.77,0:30:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“用克丘亚语向你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.88,0:30:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“每一个人问好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.66,0:30:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.60,0:30:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）“你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.64,0:30:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）“你好 愿到处都有和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.48,0:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“无论你们是谁 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“我们对你们心怀善意”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.05,0:30:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“并带着和平穿梭星际”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.72,0:30:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）“你好”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.29,0:30:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）“向每个人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.56,0:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）“向所有人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.64,0:31:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“愿和平与你们同在”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.78,0:31:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“我们代表地球的居民”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.69,0:31:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.36,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（越南语）“...致以友好的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.08,0:31:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（土耳其语）“亲爱的说土耳其语的朋友们”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.67,0:31:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（土耳其语）“祝你们有个美好的早晨”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.42,0:31:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（日语）“你好 你们好吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.32,0:31:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,（印地语）“来自地球居民的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.51,0:31:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（威尔士语）“祝你们现在及未来健康”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.69,0:31:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（意大利语）“致以最美好的祝愿和问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.50,0:31:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（僧伽罗语）“健康长寿”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（恩古尼语）“向伟大的你们致意”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.48,0:31:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,（恩古尼语）“祝你们永恒繁荣”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.32,0:31:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（塞索托语）“向伟大的你们致以问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.71,0:31:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,（吴语）“祝大家好”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.93,0:31:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚美尼亚语）“向宇宙中存在的...”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.71,0:31:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚美尼亚语）“所有生命致以问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.36,0:31:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（朝鲜语）“你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.41,0:31:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,（波兰语）“欢迎 来自异世界的生命”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.56,0:32:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,（尼泊尔语）“地球人祝愿你们拥有一个和平的未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.61,0:32:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,（汉语）“各位都好吧？我们都很想念你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.84,0:32:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,（汉语）“有空请到这儿来玩”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.98,0:32:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,（伊拉族语）“祝愿你们一切都好”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.11,0:32:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（瑞典语）“来自地球...”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.59,0:32:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（瑞典语）“伊萨卡小镇一名程序员的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.38,0:32:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（齐切瓦语）“其他星球的朋友们 你们好吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.69,0:32:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,（古加拉特语）“地球人类向宇宙各处”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（古加拉特语）“致以诚挚问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.27,0:32:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（古加拉特语）“期待着收到你们的回复”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.19,0:32:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌克兰语）“来自我们世界的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌克兰语）“祝愿你们幸福健康 长久繁荣”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.71,0:32:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（波斯语）“向遥远天际的....”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.59,0:33:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥里亚语）“来自太阳系第三颗行星...”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.10,0:33:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥里亚语）“地球的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.10,0:33:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“向宇宙所有族群致意”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“愿和平永远伴随你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.68,0:33:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（马拉地语）“地球人民向你们传递美好的祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.35,0:33:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）“太空的朋友们 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）“吃过饭没？来我们这儿坐坐”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:29.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（异步研究所雇员 纳伦·沃恩）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.21,0:33:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（匈牙利语）“用匈牙利语向宇宙中所有热爱和平的生命致意”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（泰卢固语）“说泰卢固语的人们...”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.19,0:33:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,（捷克语）“亲爱的朋友们 祝你们万事如意”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.49,0:33:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（卡纳达语）“代表说卡纳达语的人们 向你们致以美好祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“大家好 我们这里很幸福”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.55,0:33:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“愿你们那里也同样幸福”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（英语）“来自地球儿童的问候”\N{\rEng}"Hello from the children of planet Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.86,0:33:58.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【多国语问候：源自1977年旅行者号金唱片】
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.40,0:34:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（古希腊语）“你们好 无论你们是谁...”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.51,0:34:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（葡萄牙语）“愿所有人平安幸福”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.48,0:34:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,（粤语）“各位好吗？祝各位平...”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.78,0:34:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦...\N{\rEng}Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.02,0:34:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“用克丘亚语向你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“每一个人问好”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.91,0:34:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.85,0:34:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）“你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.89,0:34:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）“你好 愿到处都有和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.73,0:34:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“无论你们是谁 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.32,0:34:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“我们对你们心怀善意”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.30,0:34:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“并带着和平穿梭星际”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.97,0:34:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）“你好”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.54,0:34:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）“向每个人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）“向所有人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.89,0:34:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“愿和平与你们同在”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“我们代表地球的居民”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.94,0:35:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.70,0:35:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（越南语）“诚挚地向你们致以友好的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.33,0:35:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（土耳其语）“亲爱的说土耳其语的朋友们”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（土耳其语）“祝你们有个美好的早晨”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.67,0:35:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（日语）“你好 你们好吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.57,0:35:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（印地语）“来自地球居民的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.76,0:35:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（威尔士语）“祝你们现在及未来健康”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.94,0:35:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（意大利语）“致以最美好的祝愿和问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.75,0:35:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（僧伽罗语）“健康长寿”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.60,0:35:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（恩古尼语）“向伟大的你们致意”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.73,0:35:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（恩古尼语）“祝你们永恒繁荣”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.57,0:35:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,（塞索托语）“向伟大的你们致以问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.21,0:35:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,（吴语）“祝大家好”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚美尼亚语）“向宇宙中存在的...”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.86,0:35:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚美尼亚语）“所有生命致以问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.51,0:35:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（朝鲜语）“你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,（波兰语）“欢迎 来自异世界的生命”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.71,0:35:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（尼泊尔语）“地球人祝愿你们拥有一个和平的未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.76,0:35:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（汉语）“各位都好吧？我们都很想念你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.99,0:36:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,（汉语）“有空请到这儿来玩”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.13,0:36:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（伊拉族语）“祝愿你们一切都好”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.26,0:36:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（瑞典语）“来自地球...”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.74,0:36:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（瑞典语）“伊萨卡小镇一名程序员的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.53,0:36:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,（齐切瓦语）“其他星球的朋友们...”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁啊？\N{\rEng}Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.20,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死...\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:17.67,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（车停）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.26,0:37:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\N{\rEng}Okay, Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.39,0:39:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）“大家好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,（缅甸语）“你们好吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.91,0:39:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（希伯来语）“你好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.02,0:39:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）“你好 向大家致敬”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.53,0:39:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）“女士们先生们 晚上好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.09,0:39:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）“再见期待下次再见”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.02,0:39:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“用克丘亚语向你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.13,0:39:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）“每一个人问好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.91,0:39:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.85,0:39:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）“你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.89,0:39:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）“你好 愿到处都有和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.73,0:39:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“无论你们是谁 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.32,0:39:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“我们对你们心怀善意”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.75,0:39:37.41,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（左声道 右声道）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）“并带着和平穿梭星际”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.97,0:39:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）“你好”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.43,0:39:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（基洛纳区-监视点J3 1990年6月29日）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.54,0:39:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）“向每个人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.81,0:39:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）“向所有人致以诚挚的问候”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.89,0:39:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“愿和平与你们同在”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“我们代表地球的居民”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.94,0:39:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）“欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了\N{\rEng}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.15,0:40:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,路上堵死了 我又没法早点走\N{\rEng}Traffic was hell, and I couldn't leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.24,0:40:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 趁还有时间聊聊吧\N{\rEng}Let's just use the time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.35,0:40:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样 克拉克？\N{\rEng}How are you today, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.70,0:40:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 我看起来怎么样？\N{\rEng}How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.95,0:40:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 可能有点累吧\N{\rEng}Fine. A little tired, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.62,0:40:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直糟糕透了\N{\rEng}I look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.24,0:40:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确认一下\N{\rEng}Can I ask, and there is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.62,0:40:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,放心回答 没什么对错\N{\rEng}no wrong answer here, you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是不是有一点喝醉了？\N{\rEng}Are you intoxicated right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么问？\N{\rEng}Why you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.28,0:40:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么问了？\N{\rEng}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我从周五起就没碰过一滴酒\N{\rEng}I haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿我这副鬼样子就是因为没喝酒\N{\rEng}It's probably why I look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.74,0:40:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能问你个事吗？ - 请说\N{\rEng}- Can I ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.27,0:40:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你把人强制关精神病院过吗？\N{\rEng}You ever 5150'd someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.27,0:40:47.18,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【加州法律5150条：强制将危险精神病人送院观察】
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.19,0:40:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年确实有过几次 只要情况需要\N{\rEng}A few times over the years, when it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.42,0:40:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那...那什么样的情况才算需要？\N{\rEng}Wh-wha-what makes it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.99,0:40:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我认为对方有伤人自残的风险\N{\rEng}If I believe that the person is a danger to themselves or others,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.43,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者无法自理\N{\rEng}or they're gravely disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.72,0:41:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.60,0:41:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.81,0:41:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\N{\rEng}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.86,0:41:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里发现了点情况\N{\rEng}I found something in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好 什么情况\N{\rEng}Okay. What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.31,0:41:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\rEng}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.96,0:41:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是个地方 我...\N{\rEng}A place. I f...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.81,0:41:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了个地方\N{\rEng}I found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.53,0:41:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,地方？\N{\rEng}A place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.38,0:41:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉...\N{\rEng}Yeah. It's like, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.50,0:41:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉店就那样...\N{\rEng}It's like the store just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.01,0:41:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,往外扩了\N{\rEng}continues, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.92,0:41:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧...店有墙\N{\rEng}It's like... you know, like there's a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.77,0:41:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,墙后头居然还是店\N{\rEng}and on the other side of the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.02,0:41:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地往外扩\N{\rEng}the store just keeps going, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 就像 像个克隆的\N{\rEng}like-like a... like a copy of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.07,0:41:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我猜入口是用镜子什么的给挡住的\N{\rEng}I-I-I figure they're using mirrors or something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.90,0:41:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\rEng}to hide the entrance, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.94,0:41:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我没听明白\N{\rEng}Sorry, I'm not following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.38,0:41:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说找到了个之前没发现的房间？\N{\rEng}Is this a room you didn't know about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.43,0:41:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.22,0:41:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是...就是你一进去后\N{\rEng}Okay, so y-y-you go in and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像个...像个写字楼\N{\rEng}at first it just looks like a- like an office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.32,0:41:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的办公室 你懂吧？\N{\rEng}Like a... like a huge office building, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.51,0:41:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...你 你继续往里走\N{\rEng}And then, uh... But then you-you keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.55,0:41:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,接着...接着你就发现\N{\rEng}and then-then you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所...所有东西都不对劲\N{\rEng}th-th-that none of it makes any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎..怎么说呢...想象一下\N{\rEng}It's-it's like, um... Imagine describing a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你给个没见过狗的人形容狗\N{\rEng}to someone who's never seen one before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.01,0:42:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\N{\rEng}and then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.53,0:42:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会画对几个地方\N{\rEng}They might get some things right, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.29,0:42:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不可能全画对\N{\rEng}but there's no way they'd get everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.08,0:42:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 诡异的在于细节\N{\rEng}You know, the devil's in the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.63,0:42:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以远看像只狗\N{\rEng}So from a distance, you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.30,0:42:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但凑近一看...\N{\rEng}you think you're seeing a dog, but then you look clos--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.72,0:42:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛那样看我？\N{\rEng}Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.76,0:42:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在试着理解\N{\rEng}I'm just trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.68,0:42:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呵\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.72,0:42:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像个心理医生 怎么表情都写在脸上\N{\rEng}You know, for a shrink, you got a terrible poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.29,0:42:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些听起来很离奇\N{\rEng}What you're saying might sound fantastical,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.01,0:42:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不危险\N{\rEng}but not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些办公室里有人吗？\N{\rEng}Are there any people in these offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.26,0:42:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过 但我能听到\N{\rEng}Not that I've seen. You know, I hear, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.37,0:42:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听到脚步声 而且...而且我一转眼\N{\rEng}There's footsteps, an-an-and stuff gets moved around
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.02,0:42:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,东西就被挪了位置\N{\rEng}when I'm not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.10,0:42:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来很离谱 但你得明白\N{\rEng}I know how this sounds, but you've got to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.82,0:42:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方太大了\N{\rEng}it's massive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.47,0:42:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像纽约地铁那么大 懂吧\N{\rEng}Like New-York's-subway-system massive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.93,0:42:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿里面有好几百人\N{\rEng}For all I know, there's hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.43,0:42:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没看到\N{\rEng}I just haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.15,0:43:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEng}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.49,0:43:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这就像个...\N{\rEng}You see? It's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.01,0:43:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就像个迷宫\N{\rEng}It's like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.79,0:43:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没尽头\N{\rEng}It just goes on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.27,0:43:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候真怕自己会迷路\N{\rEng}Sometimes I'm scared I'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.14,0:43:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么除了你 没人发现这地方？\N{\rEng}Why do you think no one else has found this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.31,0:43:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.66,0:43:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但入口在负一层\N{\rEng}The entrance is on the subfloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.02,0:43:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整个结构估计都在地下 懂吧\N{\rEng}so the whole structure is probably underground, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.97,0:43:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上根本没这个地方\N{\rEng}It's not on any city maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.32,0:43:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,入口根本看不出来 谁会想到去找？\N{\rEng}The entrances are hidden, so who'd think to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.40,0:43:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说不信你...\N{\rEng}I'm not saying I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.02,0:43:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你跟我说\N{\rEng}but you told me yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.43,0:43:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你周五就开始戒酒了\N{\rEng}you haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.34,0:43:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这会不会导致幻.... - 行了\N{\rEng}- Do you think there is a-- - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.34,0:43:36.40,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注：戒断反应可能产生幻觉】
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.42,0:43:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 停 停\N{\rEng}- Clark-- - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.31,0:43:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果这是真的... - 行 我懂了 多谢您啊\N{\rEng}- If this is true-- - Yeah, I get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早会带着证据回来\N{\rEng}You know, I'm gonna come back here with proof
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.58,0:43:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候你得给我好好道歉\N{\rEng}and you're gonna owe me a serious fucking apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.95,0:44:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\N{\rEng}Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.59,0:44:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那么早谁呀 来了 来了\N{\rEng}Jesus, goddamn, I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.45,0:44:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 克船长？\N{\rEng}- Hey. - Cap'n Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额... - 等等 等等 小凯 快来\N{\rEng}- Um... - Wait, wait, wait, wait. Kat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.28,0:44:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来了 - 快点\N{\rEng}- I'm coming. - Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.58,0:44:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我来了\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样的... - 搞什么鬼\N{\rEng}- Look-- -What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.57,0:44:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个...\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.66,0:44:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们明天有空吗？\N{\rEng}What are you guys doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.03,0:45:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.41,0:45:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我给钱 算加班 顶多两个小时 很快的\N{\rEng}I'll pay you. Two hours. Overtime. Tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.73,0:45:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,行 给钱干什么？\N{\rEng}Okay, pay us for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.19,0:45:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,做调研\N{\rEng}Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.43,0:45:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像机还在你们那儿吧？\N{\rEng}You got the camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.87,0:45:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能...能再帮我拍点东西吗？\N{\rEng}You can-you can borrow it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.86,0:45:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行？\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.80,0:45:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始拍了\N{\rEng}Okay, we are rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.30,0:45:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿摆了些东西\N{\rEng}We got, um, some shit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.74,0:45:30.62,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（车停）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.61,0:45:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还有停车牌\N{\rEng}We got some stop signs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.39,0:45:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 呃 绳子\N{\rEng}and, uh... a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.09,0:45:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,拿绳子干嘛？\N{\rEng}What's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.27,0:45:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,装备\N{\rEng}Supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.57,0:45:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 看来咱们要被他绑了\N{\rEng}Oh, great, he's gonna tie us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我绑 是要给自己绑好\N{\rEng}No, we're gonna tie ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.34,0:45:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 挺重口味的\N{\rEng}Hmm. Kinky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.24,0:45:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡说什么\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你还没说清楚\N{\rEng}Uh, you still haven't told us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.65,0:45:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这儿干嘛？\N{\rEng}what we're doing here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.71,0:45:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 做调研\N{\rEng}I did tell you. Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.67,0:45:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是调研装备\N{\rEng}These are supplies, and we're using them for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.68,0:45:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么难理解吧\N{\rEng}It's not that hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.47,0:45:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,行 研究什么？\N{\rEng}Okay, research for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.57,0:45:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你得具体点 老哥\N{\rEng}Y-you gotta be more specific, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.85,0:45:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进门了\N{\rEng}I'm gonna go through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.20,0:46:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么门？\N{\rEng}What door?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.59,0:46:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是门\N{\rEng}That's the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.71,0:46:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在另一边也贴了框\N{\rEng}I taped an outline on the other side, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.49,0:46:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以防咱们找不到\N{\rEng}just to help us find our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.78,0:46:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博？ - 怎么了？\N{\rEng}- Bobby? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.12,0:46:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这很离谱 但得听我的\N{\rEng}Look, I know it sounds crazy, but follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.51,0:46:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.29,0:46:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在天亮前赶回来\N{\rEng}I want to be back before sunup.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.27,0:46:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 现在才晚上九点 你说什么...\N{\rEng}Dude, it's like 9 p.m. What the fuck are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.89,0:46:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 克拉克 - 卧槽\N{\rEng}- What the fuck! Clark?! - What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.93,0:46:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么做到的？ - 老哥 你...\N{\rEng}- How did you do that? - Dude, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.41,0:46:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了吧？他怎...怎么会...\N{\rEng}Did you fucking see that?! H-how did he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.89,0:46:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿 快进来看看\N{\rEng}I'm right here. Come see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.96,0:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 你居...居然真的...\N{\rEng}What the fuck? D-did you just fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.27,0:46:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？怎么会...\N{\rEng}What? How the f...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.92,0:46:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢？阿博 快住手\N{\rEng}Bobby, stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.05,0:46:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卧槽 - 克拉克 你在哪儿？\N{\rEng}- What the fuck?! - Clark, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.36,0:46:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你...你看到了没？\N{\rEng}Ha! Hey, did you... did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.13,0:46:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他钻哪去了？ - 看到了 阿博 我看到了\N{\rEng}- Where the fuck did he go? - Yes, Bobby, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.66,0:46:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 搞什...\N{\rEng}Oh! Where the f--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.41,0:46:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,踏进来就行 没事的\N{\rEng}Just step through the door, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.49,0:46:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了吧 你得先解释清楚\N{\rEng}What?! No! Tell us what is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.85,0:46:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 直接...\N{\rEng}You know what, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.95,0:46:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 阿博 别进去 阿博 快停下 你要干什么？\N{\rEng}No, Bobby, wait! Bobby! Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.14,0:46:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\N{\rEng}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.41,0:46:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我去啊\N{\rEng}What the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.43,0:46:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥\N{\rEng}Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.55,0:46:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 这怎么可能？\N{\rEng}Dude, how is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.15,0:47:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博 克拉克 - 行...\N{\rEng}- Bobby! Clark! - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.46,0:47:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪？里面到底是什么地方？\N{\rEng}Where are you? What the fuck is back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.00,0:47:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 小凯 没事的\N{\rEng}No, no, no, Kat, it's good, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.37,0:47:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧...赶紧进来看看\N{\rEng}J-just, you gotta come see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.81,0:47:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...对 你看...\N{\rEng}I mean... Right, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.92,0:47:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这 呃...\N{\rEng}You see, it's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.30,0:47:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 克拉克 这是什么地方？\N{\rEng}- It's fine. - Clark, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.67,0:47:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在哪？ - 哦\N{\rEng}- Where are we? - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.48,0:47:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正想弄明白呢\N{\rEng}That's what I'm trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.37,0:47:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是谁的破烂？\N{\rEng}Whose, um... Whose shit is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.78,0:47:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是你...是你店里的吗？\N{\rEng}Is it-is it... is it part of your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.80,0:47:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有主人的话\N{\rEng}If it belongs to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.07,0:47:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没碰到那个人 - 好吧\N{\rEng}- I haven't met them yet. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,自从发现这地方 我每晚都来\N{\rEng}I've been in here every night since I found the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.49,0:47:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但也就看了个冰山一角\N{\rEng}and I still barely scratched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.78,0:47:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,走 我带你们看看\N{\rEng}Come on. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.25,0:47:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,越往后越有意思\N{\rEng}It only gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.75,0:47:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真扯... - 嘿 嘿\N{\rEng}- What the fuck... - Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.99,0:47:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他别给咱们下药了吧？\N{\rEng}You don't think he, like, dosed us or something, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.55,0:47:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,药？没那回事 咱们没嗑药\N{\rEng}What? No, no, no. We're not on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.65,0:47:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要是嗨了 我肯定能感觉到\N{\rEng}I think I'd be able to tell if I was high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.19,0:47:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就嗨着呢\N{\rEng}You are high!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.29,0:47:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哈草不算\N{\rEng}Pot doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.25,0:47:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...这就像...\N{\rEng}So, um, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.67,0:47:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,像个空办公区？\N{\rEng}what, like an empty office building?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.08,0:47:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿？算是吧 但这地方简直像是\N{\rEng}In here? Sure. But it's like it was made
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.39,0:47:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一帮嗑嗨了的建筑工盖出来的\N{\rEng}by a bunch of construction workers on acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.84,0:48:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还搞了个泳池\N{\rEng}There's even a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.58,0:48:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有泳池？\N{\rEng}There's a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.91,0:48:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 算是吧\N{\rEng}Yeah. I mean, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.01,0:48:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟上\N{\rEng}Keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.30,0:48:07.46,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（车停）
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.15,0:48:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“车停”什么鬼？\N{\rEng}"Pots." What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.65,0:48:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 那是我上次走的路\N{\rEng}Yeah, no, no, that's the way I went last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.76,0:48:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我想找个楼梯下去什么的\N{\rEng}Yeah, when I was looking for a staircase down or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.76,0:48:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,结果只发现了个...\N{\rEng}Only thing I found so far is basically more of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.69,0:48:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好的...\N{\rEng}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.47,0:48:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 其实就是个斜坡\N{\rEng}I don't know, it's like a ramp, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.79,0:48:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿...就在前面\N{\rEng}It's, uh... It's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.11,0:48:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了\N{\rEng}We'll be at it in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.85,0:48:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.47,0:48:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面总共有多少层？\N{\rEng}How many floors does it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.09,0:48:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能挖...\N{\rEng}Is this not technically...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.99,0:48:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 开始拍了吗？\N{\rEng}Okay. All right, you filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.05,0:48:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拍了  - 行\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.17,0:48:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得让阿博下去？\N{\rEng}I don't see why Bobby has to be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.06,0:48:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想去 - 摄像机在他手上\N{\rEng}- I want to. - He's the one with the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.88,0:48:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,相机又没长在他身上\N{\rEng}Well, it's not like it's attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.72,0:48:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它挂在我学生证上的 所以就算长在身上了\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, I mean, to my student ID, yeah, it kinda is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.29,0:48:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是觉得不对劲 就拽一下 我把你拉上来 明白吧？\N{\rEng}Any trouble, just give a tug, and I'll pull you up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.60,0:48:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不对劲？克拉克 下面有什么不对劲？\N{\rEng}Trouble? Clark, what fucking trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.27,0:48:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\N{\rEng}There's not going to be any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.48,0:48:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 宝贝 没事\N{\rEng}Babe, babe, babe, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.63,0:49:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别下... - 真的没事 我没问题\N{\rEng}- No, hey-- - It's good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.45,0:49:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你不用下去\N{\rEng}Baby, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.92,0:49:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我就是想看看下面有什么\N{\rEng}No, it's cool. I-I just want to see what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.69,0:49:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不好奇吗？ - 简直是疯了\N{\rEng}- Are you not curious? - This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.91,0:49:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能走多远就走多远 - 没事 你看 你看\N{\rEng}- Just go as far as you can. - No, look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.64,0:49:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不用绳子也能走下去\N{\rEng}You can basically walk down without a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.51,0:49:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 一点也不陡\N{\rEng}It's fine, and it's not even steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.56,0:49:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.33,0:49:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 但有一件事\N{\rEng}Okay, just don't... just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.76,0:49:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我回不来 记得告诉我妈我爱她哦\N{\rEng}If I don't come back, you'll tell my mom I love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.64,0:49:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 - 那么 走吧\N{\rEng}- Okay. - All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好 慢慢来\N{\rEng}All right, just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.49,0:49:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.34,0:49:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 实际上还挺陡的\N{\rEng}Oh, it is actually kind of steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.76,0:49:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题吧？ - 没问题\N{\rEng}- You good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.17,0:49:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拉紧点 别把我摔了 - 放心\N{\rEng}- Just, uh... try not to drop me. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.60,0:49:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要放绳子告诉我\N{\rEng}Tell me how much you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.04,0:49:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...慢点\N{\rEng}Whoa... Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.36,0:49:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么...喔 喔 喔 操 啊\N{\rEng}What the... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Fuck! Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.96,0:49:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你会不会放绳子\N{\rEng}What the fuck are you guys doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.07,0:49:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起\N{\rEng}Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.17,0:49:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子绕到床腿上了\N{\rEng}It was stuck around the leg of the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.86,0:49:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 行 没事\N{\rEng}- Are you okay? - Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.33,0:49:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是绝了\N{\rEng}Jesus fucking Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.00,0:50:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,继续放绳子\N{\rEng}Just keep letting me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.74,0:50:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来了\N{\rEng}All right. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.45,0:50:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我下来了\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.13,0:50:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么没？\N{\rEng}See anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.58,0:50:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\rEng}Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.71,0:50:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就是...\N{\rEng}Uh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.86,0:50:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一堆脏衣服和垃圾\N{\rEng}It's a bunch of laundry and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.09,0:50:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？衣服？\N{\rEng}What do you mean? Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.77,0:50:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这下面真是臭死了\N{\rEng}Yeah, it just fucking stinks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.69,0:50:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么吗？\N{\rEng}See anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.61,0:50:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有 呃...给我点时间\N{\rEng}Yeah, just, uh... Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.78,0:50:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.15,0:50:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真乱\N{\rEng}Oh, god...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.06,0:51:02.69,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（结束南非种族隔离）
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.34,0:51:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还撞衫了？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.69,0:51:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？\N{\rEng}Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.78,0:51:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就想确认下你没事\N{\rEng}Just checking that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.33,0:51:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事 只是 呃...\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm fine. Just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.66,0:51:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.92,0:51:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.86,0:51:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.01,0:51:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\rEng}What the fuck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.23,0:51:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？快上来\N{\rEng}Bobby? Come back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.65,0:51:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里发毛\N{\rEng}I don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.30,0:51:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 呃...再多放点绳子\N{\rEng}Hey! Uh... Let some more line out!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.19,0:51:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 已经到头了\N{\rEng}I can't! It's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.33,0:51:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.00,0:51:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卧槽 卧槽 卧槽\N{\rEng}Fuck! Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.09,0:51:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉我上去 拉我上去 快\N{\rEng}Pull me up! Pull me up! Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.51,0:52:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 怎么了？\N{\rEng}Bobby! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.05,0:52:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操 - 你看到了什么？\N{\rEng}- Fuck! - What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.88,0:52:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么 快把他拉上来\N{\rEng}What the fuck is it? Pull him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.22,0:52:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在拉啊 我的天 - 操\N{\rEng}- I am! Jesus Christ! - Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.73,0:52:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拉快点\N{\rEng}Pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.54,0:52:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉 老哥 搞什么鬼\N{\rEng}Pull, man! What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.06,0:52:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绳子绕到我脚上了 - 操\N{\rEng}- It's getting caught on my feet! - Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.72,0:52:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绳子绕到... - 快点使劲拉\N{\rEng}- I can't pull-- - Fucking pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.54,0:52:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 快点拉\N{\rEng}Clark, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.60,0:52:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了 快到了 宝贝 坚持住\N{\rEng}Almost here! Almost here, babe, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.10,0:52:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快把他拉上来 - 你看到了什么？\N{\rEng}- Pull him up! - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.33,0:52:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下...下面有人 - 你安全了...\N{\rEng}- There's, uh, there's someone down there. - We've got you--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.32,0:52:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？- 操\N{\rEng}- What? - Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.57,0:52:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点说 深呼吸 宝贝 没事了\N{\rEng}Slow down, just breathe. Baby, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.09,0:52:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这破玩意儿给我解开 操 真是够了\N{\rEng}Just get this shit off me, man. Fuck. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.97,0:52:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事了 没事了 来 - 你看到了什么？\N{\rEng}- It's okay. It's okay. Here. - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.63,0:52:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 深呼吸 - 这打的什么破结？\N{\rEng}- Hey, deep breath. - What kind of knot is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.77,0:52:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卧槽 - 哎 哎 哎\N{\rEng}- What the fuck?! - Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.31,0:52:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快救命 克拉克 - 抓紧我\N{\rEng}- Help us! Clark! - Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.78,0:52:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来了 来了 来了 - 救人啊 你个混蛋\N{\rEng}- Okay, okay, okay! - Help, you fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.85,0:52:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我解 - 快给我解开 老哥\N{\rEng}- Let me get it! - Untie me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.94,0:52:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你特么在磨蹭什么？\N{\rEng}What the hell are you doing, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.44,0:52:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我解不开 - 快点 克拉克\N{\rEng}- I can't! - Hurry, Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.43,0:52:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在弄了 我在弄了 - 操\N{\rEng}- I'm trying, I'm trying! - FUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.62,0:52:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别松手 别松手\N{\rEng}Don't let go! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.89,0:52:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坚持住 - 操 千万别放手\N{\rEng}- Hold on! - Fuck! Don't let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.81,0:52:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 千万别放手 - 我去拿...\N{\rEng}- Don't let me go! - Let me get at--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.30,0:52:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\N{\rEng}BOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.43,0:52:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小凯 不\N{\rEng}NO! KAT, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.07,0:52:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\N{\rEng}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.16,0:52:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\N{\rEng}BOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.79,0:52:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\N{\rEng}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.56,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 我们得...克拉克\N{\rEng}What are we doing? We need to... Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.99,0:53:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 别 别 别\N{\rEng}Bobby! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.55,0:53:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别 小凯 小凯\N{\rEng}Ow... KAT! Kat...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.57,0:53:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\N{\rEng}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.26,0:53:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\N{\rEng}Bobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.01,0:53:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\N{\rEng}Bobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.11,0:53:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\N{\rEng}Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.83,0:53:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.70,0:53:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不 不 不 不 不\N{\rEng}Oh, no, no, no, no, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.24,0:54:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\N{\rEng}Kat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.33,0:54:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\N{\rEng}Kat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.74,0:55:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.86,0:55:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来 滚开\N{\rEng}Stay back! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.83,0:56:27.01,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（麦基路）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.44,0:56:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？克拉克\N{\rEng}Clark? CLARK!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.42,0:56:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿...\N{\rEng}I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.99,0:56:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这 那东西要回来了\N{\rEng}I'm here! It's gonna come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.58,0:57:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快让我进去 克拉克 求你让我进去\N{\rEng}Please, Clark, please let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.75,0:57:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小凯？ - 让我进去\N{\rEng}- Kat? - Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.89,0:57:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你在在哪？\N{\rEng}Wh-wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.09,0:57:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走 克拉克 没时间了\N{\rEng}We have to go now, Clark! We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.10,0:57:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那东西要回来了 它会找到我的 - 小凯 小凯？额...\N{\rEng}- It's gonna come back, it's gonna find me! - Kat! Kat? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.52,0:57:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我没搞明白 你到底在哪？\N{\rEng}Wait, I don't understand. Wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.31,0:57:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 赶紧让我进去\N{\rEng}Please, let me the fuck in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.82,0:57:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但这...这是堵墙啊\N{\rEng}But it's a... it's-it's a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.36,0:57:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能看到我？\N{\rEng}How can-how can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.40,0:57:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我在玻璃的另一边\N{\rEng}I'm on the other side of the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.48,0:57:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看不见我？\N{\rEng}How can you not see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.28,0:57:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么玻璃？你在说什么鬼话？\N{\rEng}What glass?! What the fuck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.42,0:57:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在...在说什...？\N{\rEng}Wh-what are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你那边能看到什么吗？\N{\rEng}Okay, can you see anything on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.81,0:57:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有门把手吗 还是有门？有没有入口之类的东西？\N{\rEng}Can you see a handle, a door? Is there a hatch, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.37,0:57:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有...\N{\rEng}No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.73,0:57:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...好吧 让我想想办法 好吗？等一下\N{\rEng}Uh... Okay. Let me figure this out, okay? Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.14,0:57:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 行吗？只是...\N{\rEng}Hold on, okay? It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.14,0:57:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克？ - 别急 别急 让我试...\N{\rEng}- Clark? - No, no, just let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.30,0:57:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 别急\N{\rEng}- Clark! - Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.30,0:57:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我找找看 - 克拉克！\N{\rEng}- Let me figure this out! - CLARK!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.40,0:57:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别催我 我在想办法 - 克拉克 快跑\N{\rEng}- Let me figure this out... - Clark! Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.39,0:57:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 它就在你身后\N{\rEng}Clark, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.04,0:58:11.20,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（诺拉·克莱...\N氯丙...）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.22,0:58:12.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【氯丙嗪：抗精神病药物】
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.76,0:59:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 住手\N{\rEng}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.35,0:59:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\rEng}Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.33,0:59:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\N{\rEng}what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.16,0:59:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过绝对 绝对\N{\rEng}I never, ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.10,0:59:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能出门\N{\rEng}ever said you could go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.97,0:59:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行\N{\rEng}It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.71,0:59:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,外面到处都是\N{\rEng}They're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.15,1:00:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“您拨打的是玛丽·克莱因医生的电话”\N{\rEng}"Hi, you've reached Dr. Mary Klein."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.41,1:00:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“我目前不便接听”\N{\rEng}"I'm not able to answer the call,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.83,1:01:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“请留言”\N{\rEng}"so please leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.38,1:01:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会尽快给您回电”\N{\rEng}"and I'll get back to you as soon as I can."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.08,1:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“玛丽...”\N{\rEng}"Mary...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.34,1:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“我打开那扇窗了”\N{\rEng}"I opened the window."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.09,1:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“我不会再回来了”\N{\rEng}"I won't be coming back."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.13,1:02:01.14,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（克船长的家具帝国）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.02,1:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“...求你了”\N{\rEng}"...Please!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.61,1:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“救救我们”\N{\rEng}"Save us!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.36,1:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（1983年 异步研究所获得120万美元联邦资助开发下一代核磁共振设备）]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.96,1:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“好 我照做”\N{\rEng}"All right! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.41,1:02:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会救你们 我会照做”\N{\rEng}I'll save you! I will do it!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.01,1:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“梦翠儿！”\N{\rEng}"Moon Child!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.01,1:02:27.01,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【电影《大魔域》1984：讲述一个男孩通过想象力重建世界的奇幻故事】
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.01,1:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你手之前碰过什么\N{\rEng}I don't know where that hand's been.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.01,1:02:30.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《大魔域》英文片名：直译为“永不结束的故事”】
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.13,1:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“哟 伙计们 瞧瞧这儿啊！”\N{\rEng}"Well, ahoy there, mateys!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.79,1:02:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“按照这藏宝图”\N{\rEng}"Now, according to me map,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.60,1:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“咱们现在已经登上了这片宝地”\N{\rEng}"we've landed on the crystal shores of a bountiful land,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.25,1:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“这里的折扣简直是在倒贴啊！”\N{\rEng}"a land filled with great deals."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.46,1:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,“你也赶紧赶紧抛锚靠岸！”\N{\rEng}"So drop your anchors and come on down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.46,1:02:49.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（圣克拉拉谷最低价\N地址国会路与麦基路口）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.87,1:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,“快来克船长的家具帝国！”\N{\rEng}"to Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.65,1:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,“潜入这顶级家具的海洋吧”\N{\rEng}"Get lost in an endless sea
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.94,1:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“桌椅沙发 卧室全套 样样齐全！”\N{\rEng}"of quality tables, chairs, couches, and bedroom sets."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.37,1:03:02.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（地址国会路与麦基路口）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.79,1:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“想给小海盗们配上下铺？”\N{\rEng}"Need bed bunks for the scallywagses quarters?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.54,1:02:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“来这儿就对了！”\N{\rEng}"W've got it all!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.91,1:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,“价格低到...”\N{\rEng}"And at prices so low
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.77,1:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,“你都觉得在抢我的钱啊！”\N{\rEng}"you'll think that yo're robbing me!"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.53,1:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.46,1:03:36.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.22,1:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.05,1:04:02.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.26,1:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\N{\rEng}Clark?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.23,1:04:21.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（无需信用卡）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.54,1:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Clark, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.78,1:04:25.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（由此下楼）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.13,1:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\N{\rEng}Clark?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.76,1:05:11.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（车停）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.74,1:05:26.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（门 和 家具店）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.93,1:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\N{\rEng}Clark?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.80,1:09:38.75,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（平面图又变了 屋顶不对 屋顶绝对不对）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.77,1:09:44.01,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（这图纸是谁签的名？但这笔迹 像我的）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.34,1:09:51.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（管他的什么超自然 理智点吧）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.78,1:09:55.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（此刻和此地是相通的）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.73,1:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\N{\rEng}Clark?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.06,1:10:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你总算发现了\N{\rEng}You found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.94,1:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不出来？\N{\rEng}Why are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.83,1:10:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你太刺耳了\N{\rEng}You were being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.66,1:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\N{\rEng}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.17,1:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里...\N{\rEng}It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.90,1:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是所有存在过的地方\N{\rEng}...every place that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.84,1:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿多久了？\N{\rEng}How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.14,1:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音？\N{\rEng}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.17,1:11:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\rEng}Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.04,1:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里只有我\N{\rEng}It's only me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.22,1:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我的\N{\rEng}You know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.84,1:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.90,1:12:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这全是为你好\N{\rEng}This is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.83,1:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在现实生活中\N{\rEng}As you walk through life,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.13,1:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,缺乏引导的心灵 总会走入死循环 养成固有的习惯\N{\rEng}the untrained mind accumulates loops, habits...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.50,1:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总是重蹈覆辙\N{\rEng}...behaviors that keep you drifting in circles,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.04,1:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入相同的问题\N{\rEng}creating the same problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.16,1:14:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总是用同样的办法\N{\rEng}reaching for the same solutions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.83,1:14:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍又一遍\N{\rEng}over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.03,1:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟神经通路就爱走阻力最小的路径\N{\rEng}Still, it's the neural pathway of least resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.00,1:15:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这条路径是我自己铺的\N{\rEng}The one I made.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.83,1:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候\N{\rEng}The one that kept me safe...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.87,1:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这套防线保护了我\N{\rEng}when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.90,1:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你看...\N{\rEng}You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.12,1:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我学会了抢在被伤害之前 把别人推开\N{\rEng}I learned to push people away before they could hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.24,1:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在 我都成年了\N{\rEng}And, now, as an adult,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.95,1:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还是留在原地\N{\rEng}I'm still stuck right where I started.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.05,1:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个人\N{\rEng}Alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.53,1:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.00,1:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一团糟 对吧？\N{\rEng}It's a real mess. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.90,1:15:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克...\N{\rEng}Clark...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.57,1:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮你...\N{\rEng}...let me help you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.93,1:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在你做出无法挽回的事之前\N{\rEng}before you do anything you can't take back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.78,1:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\N{\rEng}Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.43,1:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 真是一团糟\N{\rEng}Yes, it's a real mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.69,1:15:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但从某种角度看 也很美\N{\rEng}But also beautiful in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.06,1:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\N{\rEng}No?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.76,1:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人是谁？\N{\rEng}Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.17,1:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方造了他们\N{\rEng}This place builds them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.28,1:16:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 其实更像是在记得他们\N{\rEng}Oh, actually, more like it remembers them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.25,1:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过记得越多\N{\rEng}And the more times it remembers something,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.69,1:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就越走样\N{\rEng}the less it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.41,1:16:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个在外面是个穿条纹衫的家伙\N{\rEng}Somewhere out there is a guy in a striped shirt,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.12,1:16:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这儿...\N{\rEng}but, in here, he's...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.98,1:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他被记成了这样\N{\rEng}remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.95,1:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有点走样\N{\rEng}Just slightly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.68,1:16:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个在外面是个...\N{\rEng}Somewhere out there is a man
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.56,1:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,坐轮椅的家伙 带了盏灯\N{\rEng}in a wheelchair, and a lamp.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.04,1:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说 这里就是这么回事\N{\rEng}I'm pretty sure that's how you get all of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.48,1:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些地方啊\N{\rEng}You know, all these places
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.57,1:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,房间和建筑啊\N{\rEng}and rooms and buildings
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.31,1:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,全都记岔了\N{\rEng}misremembering themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.02,1:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克...\N{\rEng}Clark...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.72,1:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好好谈谈吧\N{\rEng}let's talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.26,1:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,换个角度看...\N{\rEng}In some ways...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.33,1:17:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至比原件更好\N{\rEng}they're an improvement on the originals.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.98,1:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比如...\N{\rEng}For starters,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.25,1:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有任何感觉\N{\rEng}they can't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.85,1:17:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下 那样得有多自在啊\N{\rEng}Can you imagine how good that must feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.57,1:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...\N{\rEng}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.55,1:17:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没念头 没痛苦 没自我...\N{\rEng}...there's no thoughts or pain, no ego...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.58,1:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也没恐惧\N{\rEng}...no fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.04,1:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,纯粹就是...\N{\rEng}They simply...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.61,1:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿\N{\rEng}exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.97,1:17:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像...就像家具一样\N{\rEng}Like... like furniture!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.62,1:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看这儿 最绝的来了\N{\rEng}Look at this. The best part.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.35,1:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能吃\N{\rEng}You can eat them!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.68,1:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的 呃...\N{\rEng}That's my, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.21,1:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,助理\N{\rEng}assistant manager.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.36,1:18:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮她 但她就是...\N{\rEng}I tried to help her, but she just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.07,1:18:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\rEng}Clark!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.38,1:18:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我解开 我们可以聊聊\N{\rEng}If you untie me, we can talk this through,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.86,1:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让你心里好受点\N{\rEng}get you feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.09,1:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 就算解开了\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, what if I did untie you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.85,1:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样？\N{\rEng}You know, what then?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.65,1:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你顶多像个\N{\rEng}You'd run around here
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.05,1:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没头苍蝇一样到处乱窜\N{\rEng}like a chicken with its head cut off,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.57,1:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,找你的出口\N{\rEng}looking for a way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.77,1:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但你最后还是得回到这儿\N{\rEng}But you'd end up in the same place you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.53,1:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你爱说的那套路径理论一样\N{\rEng}Like the path thing you're always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.83,1:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\N{\rEng}Clark!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.61,1:19:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的想帮你 只要告诉我你想要什么\N{\rEng}I just want to help you. Just tell me what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.15,1:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我...我一定照做\N{\rEng}I'll-I'll-I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.67,1:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.40,1:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的 拜托了\N{\rEng}Yeah. Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.50,1:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.77,1:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听你亲口说\N{\rEng}Well, I want you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.18,1:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我没做错任何事\N{\rEng}that I didn't do anything wrong, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.86,1:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是你之前对我看走眼了\N{\rEng}that-that you were wrong about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.66,1:19:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是我看走眼了 是我错了\N{\rEng}I was wrong about you! I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.32,1:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我真的看错你了 - 不 不 不要这样\N{\rEng}- I was wrong about you. - No, no, not-not like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.98,1:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别这么快 好吗？\N{\rEng}Not... not so fast, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.25,1:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我想...我想先定个场景\N{\rEng}I mean, I wanna... I want to set the scene first!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.40,1:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们从...\N{\rEng}Let's start, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.55,1:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...从那晚开始\N{\rEng}well, the night that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.81,1:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我被撵出我自己家的那晚\N{\rEng}that I got kicked out of my own house.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.94,1:19:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.62,1:20:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 嗯...很晚了\N{\rEng}It was, um... It was late.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.84,1:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里很暗\N{\rEng}A lot darker.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.24,1:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\rEng}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.72,1:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,关下灯\N{\rEng}Lights, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.33,1:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,之前跟她试过\N{\rEng}I tried this exercise with her before.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.56,1:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她根本不会动 结果都一样\N{\rEng}It doesn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.21,1:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.74,1:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己来\N{\rEng}I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.97,1:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 这终究还是我的房子\N{\rEng}It's still my house after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.47,1:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.34,1:20:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 这样才对\N{\rEng}Thank you. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.66,1:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...\N{\rEng}But there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.78,1:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还是...\N{\rEng}still...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.94,1:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,缺点儿什么\N{\rEng}something off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.24,1:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 求你..\N{\rEng}Clark, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.86,1:21:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 拜托 不要 不要...\N{\rEng}No, please, don't, don't...!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.89,1:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.11,1:22:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.59,1:22:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把杯子打碎了 还把你吵醒了\N{\rEng}broke the glass and woke you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.23,1:22:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你睡得早\N{\rEng}I know how you like to sleep early.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.53,1:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里忙太久了\N{\rEng}I was at the store late.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.19,1:22:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就忘了时间\N{\rEng}I guess I lost track of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.06,1:22:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前在对账\N{\rEng}I was checking inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.28,1:22:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...\N{\rEng}But...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.90,1:22:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,顺路去喝了一点啤酒\N{\rEng}I stopped off for a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.99,1:22:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 芭芭拉\N{\rEng}- Clark-- - Barbara!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.28,1:22:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前在对账\N{\rEng}I was checking inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.11,1:22:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后顺路去喝了一点啤酒\N{\rEng}Then I stopped off for a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.16,1:22:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一点...一点是多少？\N{\rEng}Defi-define a few.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.15,1:22:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想喝多少就喝多少\N{\rEng}As many as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.07,1:22:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这房子是我的\N{\rEng}Because this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.11,1:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷都是我在还\N{\rEng}I pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.67,1:22:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的钱都是我在出 你上学是我供\N{\rEng}I pay for everything. I pay for you to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.53,1:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,休学也是我供\N{\rEng}I pay for your time off school!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.93,1:23:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,连住这儿都是我在供\N{\rEng}I pay for the roof over your head!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.60,1:23:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要孩子 对吧？\N{\rEng}You want kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.72,1:23:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,养孩子得花钱\N{\rEng}Well, that takes money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.99,1:23:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人去挣钱\N{\rEng}So someone has to work around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.76,1:23:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了这儿得有人干活\N{\rEng}I said someone has
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.97,1:23:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在那儿当个懒猪混吃等死\N{\rEng}to get off her fat ass and work around here!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.72,1:23:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你没考上建筑师 并不代表...\N{\rEng}Just because you didn't get to be an architect don--
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.94,1:23:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老子就是建筑师\N{\rEng}I am a fucking architect.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.11,1:23:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以得成天在那破店里卖这些玩意儿\N{\rEng}I'm just stuck selling shit furniture because someone
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.61,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为某个懒猪在家混吃等死 根本不肯出力！\N{\rEng}won't get off her fat fucking ass and help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.37,1:23:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我才不是你老婆 - 别出戏\N{\rEng}- I'm not your wife! - Stay in character.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.48,1:23:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,继续演\N{\rEng}Stay in character!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.37,1:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我压根就没见过她 - 继续演你的角色\N{\rEng}- I've never even met her! - STAY IN CHARACTER!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.59,1:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,滚你妈的蛋！\N{\rEng}FUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.21,1:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\rEng}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.03,1:23:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道为什么你老婆甩了你吗？\N{\rEng}You wanna know the real reason your wife left you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.85,1:23:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不是因为酗酒\N{\rEng}It wasn't the drinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.50,1:23:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是半夜烂醉回家 甚至不是你的坏脾气\N{\rEng}or the stumbling home at all hours, or the rage.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.12,1:23:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你是个巨婴\N{\rEng}It was the whining!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.05,1:23:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这辈子没一件事是你的错 对吧？\N{\rEng}Nothing's ever your fault, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.40,1:23:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喝多了 赖工作\N{\rEng}You drink too much? Blame your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.66,1:23:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,恨职业 赖世界\N{\rEng}You hate your job? Blame the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.44,1:23:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被撵出家门\N{\rEng}You get kicked out of the house?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.90,1:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,赖老婆\N{\rEng}Blame your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.70,1:24:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你攻击我 绑架我\N{\rEng}You attack me and tie me up?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.06,1:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就去赖你的脑子！\N{\rEng}Blame your brain!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.29,1:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你这颗烂脑子 就是你本人 废物\N{\rEng}You are your fucking brain, you dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.40,1:24:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以 全都是我的错？ - 是啊\N{\rEng}- You're saying it's my fault? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.72,1:24:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但你肯定又要赖你的脑回路 对吧？\N{\rEng}But it's just the way you're wired, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.05,1:24:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对！\N{\rEng}ISN'T IT?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.83,1:24:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那我怎么才能停下来？\N{\rEng}How do I stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.47,1:24:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,实话实说 我一丁点的招都没有了\N{\rEng}Honestly, I have no fucking idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.73,1:24:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了你 克拉克\N{\rEng}I can't help you, Clark.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.03,1:24:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,能试的我都试了\N{\rEng}As much as I tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.47,1:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本不是我能左右的\N{\rEng}It's just not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.49,1:24:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我谁也救不了\N{\rEng}I can't save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.84,1:24:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？\N{\rEng}You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.83,1:25:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实不想改\N{\rEng}I don't think I want to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.58,1:25:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别改\N{\rEng}Then don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.98,1:25:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这里\N{\rEng}I like it in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.04,1:25:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这么久以来\N{\rEng}For the first time in a long time,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.79,1:25:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次觉得...\N{\rEng}I feel like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.80,1:25:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于找到了我的归宿\N{\rEng}like I'm right where I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.68,1:25:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那就留下吧\N{\rEng}Then stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.14,1:25:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么待着\N{\rEng}Right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.99,1:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得放我走\N{\rEng}But let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.82,1:26:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.90,1:26:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起什么？\N{\rEng}About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.03,1:26:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这儿干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.02,1:26:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是玛丽\N{\rEng}This is Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.99,1:27:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她是咱们的心理治疗师\N{\rEng}She's our therapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.34,1:27:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她正要离开\N{\rEng}She was just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.00,1:27:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEng}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.11,1:27:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用担心\N{\rEng}You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.51,1:27:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她说咱们不需要改变\N{\rEng}She says we don't need to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.93,1:27:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.82,1:27:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是咱们的脑回路\N{\rEng}It's just the way we're wired.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.96,1:31:21.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（由此下楼）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.48,1:31:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“向宇宙所有族群致意”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.95,1:31:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“愿和平永远伴随你们”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.06,1:31:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,（马拉地语）“地球人民向你们传递美好的祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.70,1:31:34.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.73,1:31:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）“太空的朋友们 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.00,1:31:41.48,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.59,1:31:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）“吃过饭没？来我们这儿坐坐”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.92,1:31:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.63,1:31:51.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（出口）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.57,1:31:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,（捷克语）“亲爱的朋友们 祝你们万事如意”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.87,1:32:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,（卡纳达语）“代表说卡纳达语的人们 向你们致以美好祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.12,1:32:07.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.56,1:32:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“大家好 我们这里很幸福”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.93,1:32:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“愿你们那里也同样幸福”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.14,1:32:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（英语）“来自地球儿童的问候”\N{\rEng}"Hello from the children of planet Earth."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.99,1:32:28.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（全店促销 低价保证 全场清空 全场甩卖）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.18,1:32:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,（古希腊语）“你们好 无论你们是谁 我们带着友谊 拜访朋友”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.29,1:32:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,（葡萄牙语）“愿所有人平安幸福”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.65,1:32:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（阿卡德语）“愿一切都很好”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.05,1:32:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（俄语）“你好 欢迎你们”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.09,1:32:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（泰语）“远方土地的朋友们 你们好...”
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.32,1:32:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）“大家好”
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.21,1:35:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？没事吧？\N{\rEng}Are you okay? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.80,1:35:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这女人是谁？\N{\rEng}Who the fuck is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.92,1:35:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\rEng}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.96,1:35:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.92,1:35:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,海盗呢？还在附近吗？\N{\rEng}What about the pirate? Can you still see the pirate?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.51,1:35:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢？他们还在后撤吗？\N{\rEng}And the other guys? Still going out the back?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.08,1:36:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（塞尔维亚语）“来自我们星球的诚挚祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.30,1:36:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥里亚语）“来自太阳系第三颗行星”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.81,1:36:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（奥里亚语）“地球的问候”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.78,1:36:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“向宇宙所有族群致意”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.25,1:36:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,（干达语）“愿和平永远伴随你们”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.36,1:36:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（马拉地语）“地球人民向你们传递美好的祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.03,1:36:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）“太空的朋友们 你们好”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.06,1:36:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,（台语）吃过饭没？来我们这儿坐坐
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.09,1:36:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,（匈牙利语）“用匈牙利语向宇宙中所有热爱和平的生命致意”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.08,1:36:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（泰卢固语）“说泰卢固语的人们向你们致以美好的祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.07,1:37:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（捷克语）“亲爱的朋友们 祝你们万事如意”
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.37,1:37:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,（卡纳达语）“代表说卡纳达语的人们 向你们致以美好祝愿”
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.06,1:37:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“大家好 我们这里很幸福”
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.43,1:37:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉贾斯坦语）“愿你们那里也同样幸福”
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.84,1:37:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（英语）“来自地球儿童的问候”\N{\rEng}"Hello from the children of planet Earth."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.46,1:37:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我叫菲尔\N{\rEng}Hello, my name is Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.50,1:38:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是玛丽 对吧？\N{\rEng}And you're Mary, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.34,1:38:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问你几个问题 主要是...\N{\rEng}Uh... I was hoping to ask you a few questions, just for...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.40,1:38:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为了核实一些细节\N{\rEng}some clarification on our end,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.61,1:38:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧？\N{\rEng}if that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.97,1:38:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 首先...\N{\rEng}Uh, first thing, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.92,1:38:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能说说 你是怎么...\N{\rEng}could you establish how you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.63,1:38:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,进来的吗？\N{\rEng}got in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.96,1:38:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿过了一家家具店\N{\rEng}I walked through a wall
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.59,1:38:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,地下室的墙\N{\rEng}in the basement of a furniture store.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.14,1:38:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这张照片 是这里吧？\N{\rEng}Can you confirm that this is the location in question?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.42,1:38:49.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（克船长的家具帝国）
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.04,1:39:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 你当时想购物 还是...\N{\rEng}Okay, good. So you were shopping, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.51,1:39:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时在找人\N{\rEng}I was looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.60,1:39:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\rEng}Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.12,1:39:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你找的那个人\N{\rEng}were you looking for this man,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.90,1:39:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是他吧？\N{\rEng}right here?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.15,1:39:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在在哪？\N{\rEng}Where am I right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.47,1:39:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我确认一下行吗？\N{\rEng}Could you just confirm for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.12,1:39:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你要找的人吧？\N{\rEng}Is this man right here the man you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.10,1:39:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.36,1:39:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 你刚才说你叫什么？ - 菲尔\N{\rEng}- Sorry, what was your name? - Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.96,1:39:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 菲尔 告诉我我现在在哪？\N{\rEng}Please, Phil. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.25,1:39:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不...\N{\rEng}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.86,1:39:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是做...呃...抱歉 我的...\N{\rEng}I make, um... Sorry, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.68,1:39:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的公司 是生产...\N{\rEng}Our company, we make...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.25,1:39:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,核磁共振成像仪的\N{\rEng}MRI machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.25,1:39:56.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（异步研究所）
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.31,1:39:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,或者...应该说\N{\rEng}Or... I should say, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.57,1:40:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经是做核磁共振仪的\N{\rEng}we used to make MRI machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.68,1:40:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不再做了\N{\rEng}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.08,1:40:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在我们...\N{\rEng}That was before we...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.90,1:40:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在我们发现那个.... - 你也进去过\N{\rEng}- Before we found-- - You've been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.15,1:40:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我去过\N{\rEng}Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.66,1:40:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这成了我的工作\N{\rEng}And now, it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.55,1:40:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我每...每天都进去\N{\rEng}Every day, I-I go in there
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.76,1:40:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,试着...\N{\rEng}and I just try to f...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.88,1:40:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,试着多弄懂一点也好\N{\rEng}try to find out ev-even a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.38,1:40:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在尽全力绘制地图\N{\rEng}I-I map out areas to the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.18,1:40:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 我越来越坚信\N{\rEng}And more and more, I'm convinced
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.63,1:40:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们有生之年\N{\rEng}that nothing in our lifetime, Mary,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.62,1:40:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,甚...甚至在整个人类记录的历史中\N{\rEng}n-nothing in-in maybe all of recorded history
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.11,1:40:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么比这更重要了\N{\rEng}means more than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.84,1:40:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是没搞明白\N{\rEng}But I don't understand it. I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.11,1:40:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我根本说不上来\N{\rEng}I-I can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.49,1:41:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这...\N{\rEng}It...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.88,1:41:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这就好比给个没见过狗的人形容狗\N{\rEng}It's like describing a dog to someone who's never seen a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.51,1:41:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\N{\rEng}And then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.45,1:41:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你想让我...形容它\N{\rEng}Now you want me to... describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.65,1:41:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你记下来 之后呢？\N{\rEng}And then you'll write it down, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.83,1:41:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 玛丽... - 之后我就能走了吗？\N{\rEng}- Mary-- - You'll let me go?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.80,1:41:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,其实咱们想的一样\N{\rEng}We all want the same thing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.45,1:41:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rEng}We do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.71,1:41:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们都只想 哪怕能多弄懂一点点\N{\rEng}We just want to find out even a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.72,1:41:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔 我最后会怎么样？\N{\rEng}What's gonna happen to me, Phil?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.34,1:41:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我能左右的\N{\rEng}That decision's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.18,1:41:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那...\N{\rEng}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.29,1:41:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们能不能就简单聊聊 就咱俩\N{\rEng}if we could just talk, just you and me,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.27,1:41:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就像...就像普通人那样\N{\rEng}you know, just like... just like two regular people.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.09,1:41:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们摊开聊聊 毕竟咱俩都进去过\N{\rEng}We could unpack some of this, we've both been in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.10,1:41:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样咱...咱们才能把话说到一块儿去\N{\rEng}and-and-and get on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.15,1:42:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在到处都在打开门\N{\rEng}There are doors opening everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.19,1:42:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搞不懂是啥把这些连在一起的\N{\rEng}We don't know why or what's connecting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.49,1:42:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地出现\N{\rEng}They sort of keep happening, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.91,1:42:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完全不知道怎么让它停下来...\N{\rEng}and we don't know how to stop them...
